data.title: Load Shedding Program
data.meta_description: Load Shedding Program - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document provides a load shedding schedule for PESCO from January 2018. It lists 50 feeders with their grid station, type (urban, rural, etc.), category based on AT&C percentage from July-September 2017, and intended duration of load shedding in hours for each category. The categories range from I (below 10% AT&C) to VIII (above 80.1% AT&C) with increasing hours of scheduled load shedding from 0 to 12 hours.
